n\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1086980/extras/c1d0538a00b4f2b212b9e70cb7718d61.poster.avif?t=1669291752\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1086980/extras/c1d0538a00b4f2b212b9e70cb7718d61.webm?t=1669291752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1086980/extras/c1d0538a00b4f2b212b9e70cb7718d61.mp4?t=1669291752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Online Multiplayer</strong></h2>Players can create rooms, and also navigate existing rooms to join other players to play together online.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1086980/extras/6a81927d0c37d63b58633173b90b3c64.avif?t=1669291752\" width=600 height=194 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Local Multiplayer</strong></h2>Compete against your friends as a space combatant to see who is the best human hunter of all!  You can play with friends locally in free-for-all or team oriented matches.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Arcade</strong></h2>A classic-style Arcade mode that tell stories of each character and what they have been promised in joining Nebulas Lasso. Some compete to reclaim lost glory, others compete to avenge their conquered race, while others simply enter for the joy of the hunt.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1086980/extras/bb9e009988f68083313cd682e0dd8d79.poster.avif?t=1669291752\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1086980/extras/bb9e009988f68083313cd682e0dd8d79.webm?t=1669291752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai